name: VOCALOID3 Project File
summary: Learn about .VSQX files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: The VSQX file replaced the .VSQ file used by previous versions of VOCALOID. The VSQX file format features several improvements, which includes the capacity to save more data and VOCALOID3 engine details.
NOTE: VOCALOID3 supports the newer VSQX file and the older VSQ file.

description: A VSQX file is a project file created by VOCALOID3, an application used to make and arrange synthesized vocals. It stores musical notes, lyrics, and vocal data for each note that are emulated by synthesized voices in VOCALOID3.
